Note (1) The maximum height of structures shall not exceed the higher of:
(a) 26 feet above the regulatory flood elevation; or
(b) 35 feet above the mean elevation.
llm_output.rationale: This note provides a general height limit that applies to multiple zoning districts, including R-8. It does not specify a unique height limit for R-8, but rather gives two options for calculating the maximum height.
llm_output.answer: 35 ft above mean elevation or 26 ft above regulatory flood elevation, whichever is higher
